---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Playbooks and Checklists for Small Business Owners"
description="Download plug-and-play AI playbooks and checklists designed for small business owners. Streamline operations, automate tasks, and save time with actionable workflows.">
	<!-- Blue Hero/Header Section -->
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
			<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-16">Playbooks & <span class="text-gradient">Checklists</span></h1>
			
				<p class="text-white text-xl mb-8">Every day, there’s a new tool, a new shortcut, a new AI promise.
But no one’s showing how to actually plug this stuff into your business.
Not just marketing. Not just chat prompts. Real operations. Real workflows.</p>
<p class="text-white text-xl opacity-80">
  These playbooks were built after helping real businesses automate real work — from scrappy startups to scaling teams with zero time to spare.
</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 text-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
      Plug-and-Play AI Playbooks for Small Business Owners Who Are Sick of Wasting Time
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
      From onboarding to emails, SOPs to SEO — these aren’t <b> "ideas." </b>They’re done-for-you workflows you can copy, customize, and deploy.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
  Whether you're a solopreneur juggling everything or a growing team ready to scale smart, these playbooks give you the unfair advantage — without the usual tech headaches.
</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8 italic">
  Used by agency owners, course creators, consultants, and ecom brands already saving hours each week.
</p>
    <a href="/downloads/ai-playbooks.zip" download class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
      Download All 10 AI Playbooks
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gray-200 py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">What You’ll Get Inside</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
      You’re not downloading some fluffy checklist. You’re getting a real-world starter kit for integrating AI into your business ops — built to work, even if you're not techy.
    </p>
    <ul class="text-left text-gray-800 space-y-3 mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <li>✅ Step-by-step AI workflows with diagrams and links</li>
      <li>✅ Pre-written email copy and SOP templates</li>
      <li>✅ Tool recommendations (and when to avoid them)</li>
      <li>✅ High-leverage use cases for small teams</li>
      <li>✅ Smart checklists to reduce busywork</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gray-300 py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">10 Real-World AI Use Cases — Solved</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Lead Intake Automation</h3>
        <p>Capture, sort, and send new leads straight into your CRM/email list using AI and Make.com.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">AI Customer Support</h3>
        <p>Set up chatbots and knowledge bases to reduce 40–60% of support volume.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">SEO Brief Generator</h3>
        <p>Create detailed, rank-ready briefs using AI to scale your content efforts.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Internal SOP Library</h3>
        <p>Centralize SOPs in a searchable system that cuts onboarding time and reduces errors.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Smart Content Calendar</h3>
        <p>Plan weeks of content using AI-assisted workflows, not sticky notes.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Client Onboarding Checklist</h3>
        <p>Automate tasks, docs, and emails to deliver a smooth onboarding experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">First Automation Opportunity</h3>
        <p>Quickly find the highest-impact task to automate first — save hours each week.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">AI Email Drafting</h3>
        <p>Use AI to create first-draft emails and reclaim your time — without losing your voice.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Website Traffic Monitoring</h3>
        <p>Track SEO metrics with simple dashboards — no GA4 headaches required.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Repeatable Task Documentation</h3>
        <p>Turn daily tasks into clear documentation using AI — create SOPs on autopilot.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 mt-32">
  This is just the highlight reel. Each playbook breaks it down so you can move fast — no guesswork, no fluff.
</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 text-center">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">You Don’t Need More Tools</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-12">
  These aren’t some AI trend-chasing PDFs. They’re systems built for doers. For people who are drowning in busywork and know they can’t scale by working harder.  
  <br>
  Download them, plug them in, and start feeling like you cloned yourself (without the creepy science).
</p>
  <a href="/downloads/ai-playbooks.zip" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
    Steal the Playbooks NOW
  </a>
</section>

</Layout>

